    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in TCP/IP based internets.  In particular it defines objects for managing MAC bridges based on the IEEE 802.1D-1990 standard between Local Area Network (LAN) segments. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
